{{define "subject"}}Welcome to RozzDB!{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi,

Thanks for signing up for a RozzDB account. We're excited to have you on board!

For future reference, your user ID number is {{.userID}} {{.userName}} .

Please send a request to the `PUT localhost:8000/v1/users/activated` endpoint with the following JSON
body to activate your account:

{"token": "{{.activationToken}}"}

Thanks,

The RozzDB Team
{{end}}

